4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to train aspiring developers. The program spans 16+2 weeks with three classes weekly, maintaining a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. No prior coding experience is necessary, and students can choose between English and Spanish for course instruction. Participants learn vital technologies like JavaScript and Python, focusing on web development, building applications, and utilizing APIs. The course culminates in a final project presentation, enabling hands-on experience. Graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop